{"tid":1053742,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人廣源邨唔見狗？","createTime":"2019-03-09T10:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T12:47:36.000Z","uid":141429,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b3eb04f1919aef8df23e90dea83cff319c95bb6a","tid":1053742,"uid":141429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"我喺沙田廣源邨帝堡城門口見到佢，唔知佢喺咪走失，但無主人跟住，有狗帶。見到佢想過馬路，唯有幫佢攔住啲車，再拿拿林跟住佢影張相。<br />\n佢本身都跟住我，想去買麵包比佢食。點知有個妹妹一野衝出黎，嚇跑咗佢，追都追唔切，最後行咗幾圈都唔見佢。<br />\n<br />\n最後見佢係帝堡城對面，廣源邨範圍，近巴士站。<br />\n<br />\n幫推，影唔到正面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMjCSJa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMjCSJa.png&h=62cbcbbd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zzGzWx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zzGzWx.png&h=3e1e5a8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72a012fa036bbb7b619a54c1a6ee072faa42b612","tid":1053742,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1f0d440094e242edafa6a4142babc2b89d8e7a7","tid":1053742,"uid":141429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2736aa0c7a1fb3e3a418200491c071ddff97bd0","tid":1053742,"uid":153503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:24:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"855d8b9b01ae120c4d2e0c4a36de8caa43428621","tid":1053742,"uid":135652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:24:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"440a3a34be78dfa3652829ce7b5f54435b752c9a","tid":1053742,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27718ca424c3151bed4761ac169f91cf735d6d3a","tid":1053742,"uid":78418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n可能係村屋個邊啲狗狗"},{"pid":"2883c241b33065ae53b65f37f0696981426c66e6","tid":1053742,"uid":127426,"like":0,"di